    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Build us up, build us up, as with one another sup’."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hallelujah—the riches of Christ!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Build us up, build us up, as with You we all rise up."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hallelujah—the living Body!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As blended members"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of His one Body,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We, the Lord do glorify!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His Light does shine!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Reviving Life does flow!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we do see that Satan is crushed!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Bless us, Lord! bless us, Lord! All prevailing is Your blood!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hallelujah, we’re built up in love!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Consummate! Consummate! All Your purpose consummate!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hallelujah—“The fullness thereof!”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The gates of Hades"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Never will prevail"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Against the builded up church!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When we are one,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The enemy is done!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord Jesus is able to come!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Intercede! Intercede! For Your people, meet Your need!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hallelujah! Get Your Bride this way."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Have Your way! Have Your way! Do a building work we pray—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hallelujah—in our life each day!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Through the cross of Jesus,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By the Spirit filled,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We are blending, building up!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We all are one!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We are...Jerusalem!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Dear Lord Jesus, we ask You to come!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
